message.body: Hey, ##### Just got back from FL and at Beau tonight. Big party was here and left a bunch of food. Here till 11pm if you're hungry:-)
Thanks thats great! I'm at pageant and just ate but would love to pick up any leftovers for tomorrow. When could I come down?
Hey thanks again for the foods. Daniel had to hit the hay so I split. I'll see you next time I'm sure. Hope your Trip was ok.

Howdy. I got out of Beau around 10:15 and headed directly to a dog-sit I'm doing tonight & all this week on 2nd and American. Exhausted from my trip and needed of get horizontal - not much of a vacation, sadly. My mom's doing a little better, though. Happy to get you food anytime, so let me know when you're hungry:-) We should cook sometime too. We'll see each other soon, I'm sure. Have a good night!
I'm always hungry and in need of cooking lessons
Just getting off brunch and popping over to D's to say hi. I have a shit ton of roasted potatoes for you if you want 'em.
I would like some potatoes if you have extra but I'm not in the neighborhood today.
I left them at Daniel's, so maybe you can get them tomorrow:-)
No problemo. Drop me a line if you feel like grabbing a beer. I'm around most of the week.
Ok I'll let you know when I'm down that way.
